OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1779887470
OL,3,CIan Huntley's inquest suspended
OL,4,Cpending murder case
OL,6,FAn inquest hearing into the prison
OL,7,Fdeath of Soham killer Ian Huntley will
OL,8,Ffollow criminal proceedings after a
OL,9,Ffellow inmate was charged with murder,
OL,10,Fa coroner has said.
OL,12,FThe 52-year-old died in the Royal
OL,13,FVictoria Infirmary in Newcastle on 7
OL,14,FMarch after he was attacked with a
OL,15,Fmetal bar in a workshop at HMP
OL,16,FFrankland in Durham on 26 February.
OL,18,FThe County Durham and Darlington
OL,19,FCoroner Jeremy Chipperfield held a
OL,20,Fbrief hearing in Crook to find out
OL,21,Fabout progress in the case.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
