FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1779887470
OL,3,CIan Huntley's inquest suspended
OL,4,Cpending murder case
OL,6,FListed under the name Ian Kevin
OL,7,FHuntley, the hearing lasted less than
OL,8,Ffive minutes.
OL,10,FCoroner's officer Bradley King said
OL,11,FDurham Police had informed him that a
OL,12,Fdefendant will appear in court on 3
OL,13,FJune for a plea and trial preparation
OL,14,Fhearing.
OL,16,FMr King said more would be known about
OL,17,Fa potential trial date following that
OL,18,Fhearing.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1779887470
OL,3,CIan Huntley's inquest suspended
OL,4,Cpending murder case
OL,6,FThe coroner adjourned the inquest
OL,7,Funtil 15 September, when another
OL,8,Fmention hearing will be held.
OL,10,FMr Chipperfield said the law required
OL,11,Fhim to suspend his investigation once
OL,12,Fa coroner became aware that someone
OL,13,Fhas been charged with murder.
OL,15,FHuntley died from a blunt head injury,
OL,16,Fa post-mortem examination revealed.
OL,18,FAnthony Russell, 43, has been charged
OL,19,Fwith murdering Huntley at the maximum
OL,20,Fsecurity jail.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
