PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1779887470
OL,3,CIan Huntley's inquest suspended
OL,4,Cpending murder case
OL,6,FHuntley was serving a life sentence
OL,7,Ffor the 2002 murders of 10-year-olds
OL,8,FHolly Wells and Jessica Chapman.
OL,10,FThe ex-school caretaker killed the
OL,11,Fbest friends after they left a family
OL,12,Fbarbecue to buy sweets in Soham,
OL,13,FCambridgeshire, on August 4 2002.
OL,15,FHe dumped their bodies in a ditch 10
OL,16,Fmiles away.
OL,18,FThey were not found for 13 days,
OL,19,Fdespite a search involving hundreds of
OL,20,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
