OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1779887470
OL,3,CIan Huntley's inquest suspended
OL,4,Cpending murder case
OL,6,FAt the time, Huntley lived with Maxine
OL,7,FCarr, who was a teaching assistant at
OL,8,FHolly and Jessica's primary school.
OL,10,FHe denied murdering the girls but was
OL,11,Fconvicted after a trial at the Old
OL,12,FBailey in 2003. He was jailed for life
OL,13,Fwith a recommended minimum term of 40
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FCarr gave Huntley a false alibi and
OL,17,Fwas jailed for 21 months for
OL,18,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,20,FShe is now living under a new identity.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
